  "system": {
    "description": "<p>Once per round, when you hit a creature with <strong>Attack Check</strong>, you deal extra damage to the target if it&rsquo;s afflicted by 1 of the <strong>Conditions </strong>listed in the table below.</p>\n<p>The extra damage is determined by the type of <strong>Condition </strong>afflicting the target. If the target is afflicted by multiple <strong>Conditions</strong>, you only deal bonus damage for 1 of the <strong>Conditions </strong>(your choice).</p>\n<table border=\"1\"><colgroup><col><col></colgroup>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Damage&nbsp;</strong></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&nbsp;Conditions</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">+1</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Bleeding</strong>, <strong>Flanked</strong>, <strong>Grappled</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">+2</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Deafened</strong>, <strong>Exposed</strong>, <strong>Hindered</strong>, <strong>Slowed</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">+3</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Blinded</strong>, <strong>Incapacitated</strong>, <strong>Restrained</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">+4</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Paralyzed</strong>, <strong>Stunned</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">+5</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Surprised</strong>, <strong>Unconscious</strong></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
